I wrote this with my mama in mind, who is now a year free of breast cancer!!! Her battle has inspired me beyond words so I decided to sing them.  This is for all the strong women out there. “Strength doesn’t come from what you can do.  It comes from overcoming the things you once thought you couldn’t.” 
I wanna thank YouTube for the instrumental track of “Love is a Losing Game”... since I’m still learning how to produce music, this is what I resort to.  Dedicate this to the strong women in your lives!! ♥️
